
Ruby on Rails RPX Demo Application
==================================

This is a small Ruby on Rails application which demonstrates how one
might integrate a Rails application with the RPX service by JanRain,
Inc.

To set up the demo:

 (1) Install Rails 2.2.2

 (2) Install the sqlite3-ruby gem

 (3) Run rake db:migrate

 (4) Go to http://rpxnow.com/ and create an RP

 (5) In config/environment.rb, set these parameters according to the
     RPX RP configuration that you set up in (4):

     * API_KEY
     * REALM

 (6) Run script/server

 (7) Nagivate to the appropriate host and port with your browser and
     try it out.